      • getCursor

        public RowCursor getCursor​(boolean cachedInstance,
                           int key,
                           long minValue,
                           long maxValue)
        Description copied from interface: BitmapIndexReader
        Setup value cursor. Values in this cursor will be bounded by provided minimum and maximum, both of which are inclusive. Order of values is determined by specific implementations of this method.
        Parameters:
        cachedInstance - when this parameters is true, index reader may return singleton instance of cursor.
        key - index key
        minValue - inclusive minimum value
        maxValue - inclusive maximum value
        Returns:
        index value cursor
